channel.title: Error Connecting to server
channel.description: Hello, I am trying to log on to my Runescape private server. Every time I type in my no-ip and my uttorent is open, I get Error Connecting to Server. I have tried different sources (no luck), but I was able to log on at a different house using a different router. Please help me as I have been trying to log on now for 1 week.
